data.description: Pre-Inspected & a 1yr Service One Home Warranty provided by sellers! Nestled on a serene half-acre lot, this 3bd/2bth home backs to woods with wildlife galore.  Enjoy the peaceful view as you sit on a super sized deck, showcasing meticulous craftsmanship with 220-volt wiring & additional supports for added strength.  Stepping inside, an updated kitchen (2023)  boasts quartz countertops, stylish backsplash and brand-new appliances. With 2 spacious family rooms on the main there's plenty of room for the entire family to spread out.   The primary suite features bay windows, built-in wall unit that accommodates a queen size bed, large walk-in closet & a remodeled 3/4 bath (2022).  Sellers have meticulously maintained this home over the years with Service One cleaning & inspecting the HVAC system yearly.  Fireplace serviced and cleaned 02/22/2024. New Water heater 2017.  Gutter Guards installed.  Vents cleaned 2019.  Located 2miles (7min) from Offutt AFB.  Shopping/restaurants close by.
